OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJames Patterson: US author 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsorry for saying white     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fwriters face racism        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Author James Patterson has apologised  
OL,6, for saying older white writers face    
OL,7, "just another form of racism", which   
OL,8, makes it harder for them to find work. 
OL,10,FThe best-selling US writer made his    
OL,11,Fcomments to The Sunday Times last week.
OL,13,FBut following a backlash, he posted an 
OL,14,Fapology and said he did not actually   
OL,15,Fthink white writers suffered racism.   
OL,17,F"I apologise for saying white male     
OL,18,Fwriters having trouble finding work is 
OL,19,Fa form of racism," the 75-year-old     
OL,20,Fwrote on Facebook on Tuesday.          
